## What Guardrails are for

`Values.md` is the philosophy doc — what {{OWNER_NAME}} cares
about and why. `Guardrails.md` is the **SMART, structural
consequence** — the lines that don't get crossed, expressed in a
form the agency can enforce.

Values inspire. Guardrails enforce.

A Guardrail is a **prohibition statement**: "the business will
not do X." Each Guardrail has 1-3 SMART Interim Guardrails (the
leading indicators that the Guardrail is being honored) and 1-5
Guardrail-aligned Initiatives (the actual sets of skills/scripts
that produce the honoring behavior).

